{
  "video_id": "As-YfI9xVB0",
  "title": "The early Temperance movement - part 1",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 483.0,
      "end_time": 2659.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] Hi, this is\nBecca from Khan Academy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2659.0,
      "end_time": 5273.0,
      "text": "and today I'm going to be\ntalking about temperance."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5273.0,
      "end_time": 7356.0,
      "text": "So, what was the temperance movement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7356.0,
      "end_time": 9036.0,
      "text": "In this video, I'll talk a little bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9036.0,
      "end_time": 13005.0,
      "text": "about what temperance\nwas, what its causes were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13005.0,
      "end_time": 17899.0,
      "text": "and how it started to\ndevelop in the early-1800s."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17899.0,
      "end_time": 20342.0,
      "text": "Temperance was the idea\nthat Americans drank"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20342.0,
      "end_time": 23837.0,
      "text": "way too much alcohol and needed\nto temper their consumption."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23837.0,
      "end_time": 25887.0,
      "text": "It started as kind of this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25887.0,
      "end_time": 28013.0,
      "text": "that people should just\ndrink a little bit less,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28013.0,
      "end_time": 31971.0,
      "text": "they should drink less whiskey,\nless rum, less hard alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31971.0,
      "end_time": 34550.0,
      "text": "And then, slowly, it started to take on"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34550.0,
      "end_time": 36920.0,
      "text": "this kind of prohibitory character."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36920.0,
      "end_time": 39522.0,
      "text": "So, again, it was the\nidea that we just needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 39522.0,
      "end_time": 42355.0,
      "text": "to temper our alcohol consumption."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43356.0,
      "end_time": 46944.0,
      "text": "And so, how did the\ntemperance movement take root?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46944.0,
      "end_time": 49359.0,
      "text": "The temperance movement\nkinda has three main causes"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49359.0,
      "end_time": 50990.0,
      "text": "that I like to think about."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50990.0,
      "end_time": 55157.0,
      "text": "So, the three main causes were\nthe Second Great Awakening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 56211.0,
      "end_time": 58378.0,
      "text": "the Industrial Revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62385.0,
      "end_time": 63799.0,
      "text": "and growing nativism"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63799.0,
      "end_time": 68393.0,
      "text": "and, frankly, racism that\nstarted as new immigrants"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68393.0,
      "end_time": 72467.0,
      "text": "were coming to America in the early-1800s."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72467.0,
      "end_time": 75053.0,
      "text": "So, this was all kinda\nhappening right around here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 75053.0,
      "end_time": 76264.0,
      "text": "and so I'll talk a little bit more"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76264.0,
      "end_time": 79227.0,
      "text": "about each of these causes\nfor the temperance movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79227.0,
      "end_time": 81234.0,
      "text": "and how it began."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81234.0,
      "end_time": 83686.0,
      "text": "So, I'll start by talking about\nthe Second Great Awakening."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83686.0,
      "end_time": 86953.0,
      "text": "So, the Second Great\nAwakening was this time period"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86953.0,
      "end_time": 91455.0,
      "text": "in the early-1800s that\nfocused a lot of social reforms"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91455.0,
      "end_time": 95990.0,
      "text": "around capturing moral\ngood or Christian ideals"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95990.0,
      "end_time": 99478.0,
      "text": "so Christian ideals,\nhere's the little cross,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99478.0,
      "end_time": 101961.0,
      "text": "within our social institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101961.0,
      "end_time": 105951.0,
      "text": "So, this happened in\neducation, in prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105951.0,
      "end_time": 108593.0,
      "text": "in the first women's rights movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108593.0,
      "end_time": 110666.0,
      "text": "And so, this was all going on in the 1800s"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110666.0,
      "end_time": 111589.0,
      "text": "and it was about this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111589.0,
      "end_time": 113767.0,
      "text": "that we needed to be\ngood and moral people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113767.0,
      "end_time": 116633.0,
      "text": "and we needed our social\ninstitutions to reflect that."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116633.0,
      "end_time": 118996.0,
      "text": "So, temperance can be seen as a part"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 118996.0,
      "end_time": 120682.0,
      "text": "of the Second Great Awakening."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120682.0,
      "end_time": 122539.0,
      "text": "And so, down here, you can kind of see"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122539.0,
      "end_time": 124163.0,
      "text": "the Second Great Awakening image here."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124163.0,
      "end_time": 125930.0,
      "text": "This is the idea that the family"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 125930.0,
      "end_time": 130012.0,
      "text": "was also intimately affected\nby people being too drunk."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130012.0,
      "end_time": 132298.0,
      "text": "Here's the father and he's really drunk"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 132298.0,
      "end_time": 134807.0,
      "text": "and things are kind of going to mayhem."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 134807.0,
      "end_time": 136084.0,
      "text": "People were just too drunk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136084.0,
      "end_time": 139236.0,
      "text": "and this was tearing apart\nlots of different institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139236.0,
      "end_time": 142871.0,
      "text": "including the family, including education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 142871.0,
      "end_time": 144590.0,
      "text": "including the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144590.0,
      "end_time": 146179.0,
      "text": "And so, that's a good transition"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146179.0,
      "end_time": 148440.0,
      "text": "to talking about the\nIndustrial Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 148440.0,
      "end_time": 150405.0,
      "text": "So, the Industrial\nRevolution was also going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150405.0,
      "end_time": 151620.0,
      "text": "at this time period"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151620.0,
      "end_time": 154545.0,
      "text": "and people could no longer\nbe drunk on the job, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 154545.0,
      "end_time": 156703.0,
      "text": "So, people used to be artisans."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 156703.0,
      "end_time": 158443.0,
      "text": "They used to just kind\nof sit in their home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 158443.0,
      "end_time": 162494.0,
      "text": "make their shoes or sew something by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162494.0,
      "end_time": 164153.0,
      "text": "and they could be drunk while doing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 164153.0,
      "end_time": 167549.0,
      "text": "But now, if you're kind\nof in a factory setting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167549.0,
      "end_time": 169676.0,
      "text": "people were getting their fingers cut off"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169676.0,
      "end_time": 172211.0,
      "text": "by these new machines that were promoted"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 172211.0,
      "end_time": 174701.0,
      "text": "in the Industrial Revolution\nbecause they were drunk"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 174701.0,
      "end_time": 176539.0,
      "text": "while trying to operate the machinery."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 176539.0,
      "end_time": 177771.0,
      "text": "So, with this new industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 177771.0,
      "end_time": 180435.0,
      "text": "workers could no longer\nbe drunk on the job."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 180435.0,
      "end_time": 182524.0,
      "text": "And so, the final cause is this nativism"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 182524.0,
      "end_time": 185850.0,
      "text": "that people were seeing with\nnew Catholic immigrants."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 185850.0,
      "end_time": 189050.0,
      "text": "So, there were Catholic immigrants\ncoming into the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 189050.0,
      "end_time": 192567.0,
      "text": "And lots of Protestants\nwere very anti-Catholic"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192567.0,
      "end_time": 194499.0,
      "text": "and anti-immigration."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194499.0,
      "end_time": 197214.0,
      "text": "They decided that the\nCatholics were drunks."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197214.0,
      "end_time": 198653.0,
      "text": "They did drink a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 198653.0,
      "end_time": 201093.0,
      "text": "but it was definitely this\nkind of racist sentiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201093.0,
      "end_time": 204144.0,
      "text": "that was percolating within\nthe Protestant community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204144.0,
      "end_time": 207018.0,
      "text": "and this kind of aligned\nitself with the Whig Party."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207018.0,
      "end_time": 210101.0,
      "text": "So, the Whigs became more Protestant;"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 211349.0,
      "end_time": 214226.0,
      "text": "they were really big temperance people."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 214226.0,
      "end_time": 216077.0,
      "text": "And the Catholics more aligned themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 216077.0,
      "end_time": 217660.0,
      "text": "with the Democrats."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 218973.0,
      "end_time": 221906.0,
      "text": "The sentiment towards\nthese immigrant populations"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 221906.0,
      "end_time": 224739.0,
      "text": "had this kind of political effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 225727.0,
      "end_time": 228441.0,
      "text": "So, at this time, temperance\nwas starting to become"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 228441.0,
      "end_time": 230239.0,
      "text": "more of a political movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230239.0,
      "end_time": 233588.0,
      "text": "and different social groups\nwere taking this more seriously."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 233588.0,
      "end_time": 236513.0,
      "text": "There were some state-level organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 236513.0,
      "end_time": 239787.0,
      "text": "It was just becoming more\nof a social phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 239787.0,
      "end_time": 244621.0,
      "text": "In 1825, right over here,\nthis really famous preacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 244621.0,
      "end_time": 248788.0,
      "text": "Lyman Beecher, did his six\nsermons on the sins of alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 250231.0,
      "end_time": 252648.0,
      "text": "And so, these sermons in 1825"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 254598.0,
      "end_time": 257445.0,
      "text": "solidified this idea in the American mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257445.0,
      "end_time": 261391.0,
      "text": "that it was anti-Christian\nto be a huge drinker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 261391.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263522.0,
      "text": "and this idea really took root."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 263522.0,
      "end_time": 267410.0,
      "text": "This is becoming kind of\nthis larger social phenomenon"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 267410.0,
      "end_time": 269909.0,
      "text": "and there start to be\nnot just more state-level"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 269909.0,
      "end_time": 272987.0,
      "text": "or community-level\nsocieties against drinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 272987.0,
      "end_time": 275891.0,
      "text": "you see the first ever\nnational organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 275891.0,
      "end_time": 280615.0,
      "text": "So, the first national\ntemperance society was in 1826,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 280615.0,
      "end_time": 285545.0,
      "text": "down here, with the American\nTemperance Society, so the ATS."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 285545.0,
      "end_time": 287152.0,
      "text": "And I'll talk more about the ATS"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 287152.0,
      "end_time": 289279.0,
      "text": "and the kind of nationalization"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 289279.0,
      "end_time": 291964.0,
      "text": "of the temperance movement\nin the next video."
    }
  ]
}